WEBVTT


00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.574
I want someone coming to Germany to say I want to belong here, 

00:00:04.574 --> 00:00:10.094
I want to learn the language and I want to become a German citizen quickly. 

00:00:10.095 --> 00:00:12.384
That is something we wish for. 

00:00:12.816 --> 00:00:17.681
And I think then there can also be naturalization celebrations, 

00:00:17.681 --> 00:00:19.961
where the whole family comes, 

00:00:19.961 --> 00:00:25.131
where everyone wears the best clothes and where the national anthem 

00:00:25.131 --> 00:00:27.716
is played together at the castle. 

00:00:27.765 --> 00:00:31.596
That is what I envision as integration in Germany. 
